"title": "8648: enquiring of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8648: enquiring of god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Requesting from God a definite direct response to a particular question. In the OT, people are frequently said to enquire of God for knowledge or guidance, often through the intermediacy of a priest or prophet.</p>\n<h2>Enquiring of God for knowledge</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:22-Gen25:23\">GEN 25:22–25:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:17\">JDG 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:5-Judg18:6\">JDG 18:5–18:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:22\">1SA 10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Enquiring of God for guidance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:1\">2SA 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:18\">JDG 20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:23\">JDG 20:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:27-Judg20:28\">JDG 20:27–20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:2\">1SA 23:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:4\">1SA 23:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:8\">1SA 30:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:19\">2SA 5:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:10\">1CH 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:23\">2SA 5:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:14\">1CH 14:14</a></p>\n<h2>Enquiring of God through intermediaries</h2>\n<h3>Priests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:5-Judg18:6\">JDG 18:5–18:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:18-Num27:21\">NUM 27:18–27:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:10\">1SA 22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:13-1Sam22:15\">1SA 22:13–22:15</a></p>\n<h3>Prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:6-1Kgs22:9\">1KI 22:6–22:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:5-2Chr18:8\">2CH 18:5–18:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:6-1Sam9:10\">1SA 9:6–9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:6\">1SA 28:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:11\">2KI 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:11-2Kgs22:20\">2KI 22:11–22:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:19-2Chr34:28\">2CH 34:19–34:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:1-Jer21:7\">JER 21:1–21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:6-Jer37:8\">JER 37:6–37:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:7\">EZK 14:7</a></p>\n<h2>Enquiring of God by casting lots</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:24-Acts1:26\">ACT 1:24–1:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:21\">NUM 27:21</a> <em>The Urim and Thummim were sacred lots carried in the breastpiece of the High Priest's ephod</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:20-1Sam10:22\">1SA 10:20–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:36-1Sam14:42\">1SA 14:36–14:42</a></p>\n<h2>Enquiring of God in prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:1-2Chr20:17\">2CH 20:1–20:17</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Enquiring of God at the tabernacle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:7\">EXO 33:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:26-Judg20:28\">JDG 20:26–20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:3\">1CH 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:5\">2CH 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Devotion to God as a necessary prerequisite for enquiring of him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:30-Ezek20:31\">EZK 20:30–20:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:1-Ezek14:11\">EZK 14:1–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:1-Ezek20:3\">EZK 20:1–20:3</a></p>\n<h2>Failure to enquire of God displeases him and heralds disaster</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13-1Chr10:14\">1CH 10:13–10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:13\">1CH 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:21\">JER 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:4-Zeph1:6\">ZEP 1:4–1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit and enquiring of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:23-John16:24\">JHN 16:23–16:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:15\">JHN 16:13–16:15</a></p>",
